summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to Land Use and Zoning; amending Plat 226W, Page 15 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, (Ordinance 86300) to rezone certain property in Section 29, Township 26 N. Range 4, E. W.M. from Single Family Residence Medium Density (RS 7200) to Multiple Residence Low Density (RM 800) zone.
